            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Compiler's comment: Cross sections for 209Bi, 197Au,",
                "239Pu alpha absorptions are given as a function of",
                "compound nuclei excitation energies. Using the AME",
                "2016 the Q-values for 213At(a), 201Tl(a) and 243Cm(a)",
                "decays were deduced as 9254.0, 1534.0 and 6168.8 keV.",
                "These values could be used to reconstruct the alpha   C",
                "beam energies."
              ]
            }
          ],
